title: [InTheCrack.com] Set #039 To #030 Video + Pictures
description:
Small note about the image sizes of the lower numbered sets you are going to encounter.

All sets above #043 have both a "medium" and "large" photo package. Obviously I chose the "large" set everytime as both sets contain the same photos. However this is not the case with the sets #043 and below.

These have a "medium" package that contains ALL the photos of that set and a "large" package that contains only a selection of the "medium" set in a higher resolution. These were not upscaled, but obviously taken at a high resolution and downscaled to be put in the "medium" pack.

Why they did this is anyone's guess. I would guess bandwidth considerations, user preferences or simply a used to be only video production team getting the grips with photography. Anyhow I include both the unaltered "medium" and "large" photo sets so you can combine or do what you want with it.


--------------


Feel free to spread this torrent to other trackers!

Set #039 to #030 of In The Crack videos and pictures. Everything is sorted according to set number and model name. Only the pictures are zipped (otherwise this torrent would be a monstrosity of course).

So, these are some big files. I have a lot more of them (all of them actually, clocking in at 1tb+), but lets start with this and see how it goes. Keep sharing if you want to see the rest!
